        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "If TruffleHog finds a verified leak, treat it as an immediate incident: revoke the key within minutes, rotate to a new key, and audit the last 24 hours of API logs for anomalous usage patterns before the revocation."
          }
